{"tid":2490533,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖記對1位置忍無可忍！今夏拿他開刀","createTime":"2021-04-15T16:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T10:42:01.000Z","uid":34571,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a39308887c43b8b9f9653cfd0af5c8dc13b56d","tid":2490533,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"根據《全市場》的消息，祖雲達斯在今年夏天想要更換球隊的1號門將。施捷斯尼（Wojciech Szczesny）今季的表現令人失望。<br />\n<br />\n  意大利媒體稱，施捷斯尼<span class=\"red\">雖然在比賽當中很少出現低級的失誤。但他的表現有時候真的很平庸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有些撲救難度不大的射門，他也會將球漏入球網。總之，他是一名不錯的門將，但不是一名頂級門將，祖記目前需要更好的門將。<br />\n<br />\n  祖記的頭號目標是AC米蘭的當拿隆馬，這名意大利國腳與米蘭的合約將在夏天到期，目前還沒有完成續約。不管怎麼說，無論是否能夠引進當拿隆馬（Gianluigi Donnarumma），施捷斯尼下季1號門將的位置應該是不保了。"},{"pid":"4d62b5824fb7310c6a1fb95ec06d62a58a014673","tid":2490533,"uid":325309,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:04:17.000Z","msg":"因為人地射波廢所以炒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ec5dc900670af5122ccbde8bdd8e1f38489213","tid":2490533,"uid":144466,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"換左個傻鳩教練先啦"},{"pid":"20fe1619d671216706e560183b88658f5dc03abe","tid":2490533,"uid":350194,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"當年當隆馬想走俾人屌到仆街 即刻流馬尿 又想再喊過"},{"pid":"2ebe7b7e3dac31d54fe824552e9922219046deee","tid":2490533,"uid":239912,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"阿記出產既龍門都敢用<br />\n都算你祖狗命大啦 捱到而家"},{"pid":"f562384ef27264e16b9cee2e2359eb5a8829026c","tid":2490533,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"穩定左幾季啦"},{"pid":"bd4ee6901ceb56734b2a0cf88788e716e68552eb","tid":2490533,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc